data.description: Looking for the special home that has it all. No need to look further. Smiling takes place as soon as you enter the bright & airy 2 story entry way with loads of updates. Hard to find 5 br. with 1 br on main floor, perfect for any special situation. Home also includes spacious loft & basement & AWESOME sun porch. Updates include all new Stainless Steel appliances less than 1 year old. All new Granite countertops, cabinets painted all white. New light fixtures installed throughout the home. Downstairs bath completed updated. New flood lights installed around the entire home. The entire home has been painted with neutral colors. Basement has some drywall and flooring. Roof is less than 5 year old. Home is ready for you to move in.
